'''''Spacechase''''' is a [[fixed shooter]] video game for the Atari Video Computer System (later called the [[Atari 2600]]) written by Ed Salvo and published by [[Games by Apollo]] in 1981.<ref name="giantlist"/><ref name=dpinterview>{{Citation
